、歷史交易明細","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/109%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c321%2c20200422%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,109,上訴,321,20200422,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"321","JDATE":"20200422","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}